{"tid":209896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★中小型銀行為爭按揭客，供樓年齡可達85歲為止！！","createTime":"2017-04-20T14:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T14:02:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa74bdcbf2a616925fa1a7a1672e9264debec12","tid":209896,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T14:32:20.000Z","msg":"現時銀行敍做按揭年期上限為30年，而銀行針對按揭客的年齡，另設按揭年期加借款人年齡的年期上限，一般為65至75年。舉例，若客戶敍做30年按揭，年齡須低於45歲；假設客戶已達55歲，則按揭年期上限為20年(75年減55年)。近期有中小型銀行將總計年期上限延長至85年，意味容許55歲的客戶敍做高達30年按揭。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，金管局注意到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有銀行延長按揭年期加借款人年齡至85年的情況</span>，並向銀行了解相關信貸政策，以及有無偏離相關信貸政策的個案，已要求銀行於上周匯報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170420/bkn-20170420203736668-0420_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170420%2Fbkn-20170420203736668-0420_00842_001.html&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=0a0242b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170420/bkn-20170420203736668-0420_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f43b2644dff61761620bc8d3cd8181232f262bc8","tid":209896,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a944e43bded1752fa530293c97578f5fb31217c7","tid":209896,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/223607_e499f78e81c09e5f0f62859ebec097a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F223607_e499f78e81c09e5f0f62859ebec097a3.jpg&